BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:City Council holds regular business meetings on the 1st and 3r
 d Monday of every month at 7 p.m. to hear priority items\, present ceremo
 nial items\, vote on the Consent Agenda\, review the General Business Age
 nda\, and conduct public hearings. The meetings are open to the public an
 d can be streamed live or on-demand. https://www.durhamnc.gov/calendar.as
 px?EID=10440
